00:41:29.510 --> 00:41:30.510
&gt;&gt;female in audience: I'm curious what your
reentry process was like. A, what you are

00:41:30.510 --> 00:41:31.510
doing now and B, how quickly if you guys are
back in the corporate world, how quickly you

00:41:31.510 --> 00:41:32.510
got wrapped up in the rat race again?

00:41:32.510 --> 00:41:33.510
&gt;&gt;Holly Corbett: Oh we learned that just because
we come back, the same stresses and the same

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:34.510
pressures that we left behind were still there,
but how we reacted to them was very different.

00:41:34.510 --> 00:41:35.510
I think travel made us a lot more resilient
and-and we -- maybe a little bit more braver

00:41:35.510 --> 00:41:36.510
because surprisingly when we came back we
